{"tid":1821390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"23萬“on9仔女同盟會”食人血饅頭後，網民響 真·on9仔女聯盟會 爆大獲 :P花生價持續上升","createTime":"2020-01-12T08:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T05:43:17.000Z","uid":237026,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a95c23317c4cc5c1e98db1fff0e6364ac7022429","tid":1821390,"uid":237026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/621778478595733/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F621778478595733%2F&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=44b00f7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/621778478595733/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n運動中既人血饅頭案<br />\n<br />\n上一篇文講內容農場嘅禍害: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/621778478595733/permalink/622507245189523/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F621778478595733%2Fpermalink%2F622507245189523%2F&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXfS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=80ef7642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/621778478595733/permalink/622507245189523/</a><br />\n<br />\nOn9協會嘅仆街們，你點滅聲都滅唔晒，我有嘅係證據，俾人揭發唔認仲要踢走我？你哋仆街死啦。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️請大家廣傳，杜絕內容農場⚠️<br />\n<br />\n我諗你地都唔使再澄清啦，有人爆咗料俾我啦。<br />\n<br />\n果然香港on9協會係一間公司，而唔係佢所講嘅非牟利機構。<br />\n<br />\n你哋撳入去佢哋啲網址，佢哋全部都有錢收㗎。真係犀利，賣衫賺錢不特止，仲要係咁share內容農場賺錢。甚至開「香港on9協會」呢個page都有錢收，你哋個良心係邊到？<br />\n<br />\n睇嚟佢哋真係賺到盤滿缽滿。日日咁多會員like同share，仲要持續咗咁耐，賺好多下喎。<br />\n<br />\n根據爆料人俾我嘅資料，我相信on9協會會長、fu wing、Tony jaa、郭晉安都有份賺錢。（暫時未知剩餘嘅12位版主有冇錢收）<br />\n<br />\n佢哋攪嘅所有嘢都係一場生意，幫手足？收皮啦。仲要人哋屌先肯捐錢，你哋個良心係咪跌撚左呀。<br />\n<br />\nBtw，話我分化個啲自己去搵下內容農場係乜撚嘢意思，唔想搵嘅我上篇文已經feed晒啲資料俾你啦。<br />\n<br />\n我相信我出現呢篇文之後會俾人即踢，請大家back up，唔好再容忍佢哋以呢啲咁冇道德嘅方法賺錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzFCAtF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzFCAtF.jpg&h=4bfc2483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LSCaa15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLSCaa15.jpg&h=96574385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t30bEVu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft30bEVu.jpg&h=9d347b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UgZvVtT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUgZvVtT.jpg&h=8d647e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jP7aa2i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjP7aa2i.jpg&h=02737ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GoQCAt1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGoQCAt1.jpg&h=256d22ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZoD4ns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZoD4ns.jpg&h=ffba7b5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac77db942ebf73e9bf91580073e8c80e7fb4f95f","tid":1821390,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:38:17.000Z","msg":"fu wing， 請你出嚟回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9629b4f5e53e923123f4a9926ca28777ab302b88","tid":1821390,"uid":269495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T09:38:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5f9090c258a6507ef316d5870f22fc9f81bca44","tid":1821390,"uid":4345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9a718c098ca75ff47778e5b284a5a920b59a52d","tid":1821390,"uid":335719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"講左內容農場好耐 但唔明點解仲咁多人睇"},{"pid":"7d004fcc954975d74ad893d7107fd88fffc5a6d7","tid":1821390,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"洪福郎條垃圾？"},{"pid":"7efa5d3987b04c9f8431ffe87eab06a34ec3eb06","tid":1821390,"uid":350548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-